💥The National Council will provide information support to the All-Russian urban competition!🚀The 7th All-Russian competition “Ideas Transforming Cities” 2023–2024 has started.” It is aimed at involving young people in the development of urban public spaces and local areas. The information partner of the competition, aimed at supporting the national project “Housing and the Urban Environment” and the federal project “Formation of a Comfortable Urban Environment”, is the National Council of Youth and Children's Associations of Russia.❓ Who can participate?🔹young designers, urbanists, architects and artists,🔹bachelors, master's students, graduate students of leading specialized areas of study (architectural design, urban planning, design, construction),🔹all concerned citizens who want to change and improve the space of their cities and settlements. 👩‍💻👨‍💻Age categories: − from 10 to 13 years;
− from 14 to 17 years old;
− from 18 to 35 years old.❓What is accepted for the competition?🔹projects aimed at developing new public spaces and improving the quality of the urban environment;🔹ideas for improving parks, streets, pedestrian paths and playgrounds.📅The correspondence stage of the competition will end on April 20, 2024 . The final will be held from May 23 to May 25, 2024 in Moscow.🔝A professional jury will determine the winners of the competition.🥇The best young participants will be awarded tickets to the All-Russian Children's Center "Scarlet Sails" for a specialized shift of architects and urbanists "Territory of Development - Urban Environment".🥇Winners in the older age category will receive:🔹recommendations for participation in architectural expeditions and workshops;🔹internship in state corporations and architectural bureaus,🔹recommendations for local governments to implement projects in their cities and settlements.✅The All-Russian competition “Ideas Transforming Cities” is included in the list of events of the Ministry of Education Russian Federation, aimed at developing intellectual and creative abilities, for the 2023/24 academic year.✍️You can register and submit your work via this link.👀You can learn more about the competitionhere.russia-territory-of-development.rfIdeas transforming citiesVI All-Russian Competition of Young Urbanists and Architects

